se]] \n|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | [[Datamatics]] \n| rowspan=\"5\" | Mumbai <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/company-facts/datamaticsglobalservices/locations/DGS01|title=Datamatics Global Services > Location Details > Computers - Software Medium & Small > Location Details of Datamatics Global Services - BSE: 532528, NSE: DATAMATICS|website=www.moneycontrol.com}}</ref>\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n|| Nashik\n|-\n|| Bangalore\n|-\n|Puducherry\n|-\n|| Chennai\n|-\n| [[Eclerx]] \n|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Firstsource]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Bhubaneswar\n|-\n| Kolkata\n|-\n| [[Flytxt]] \n| [[Amsterdam]]\n|| Thriuvananthapuram\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Fulcrum Digital]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n| Pune\n|-\n|[[Gateway TechnoLabs]]\n|[[Ahmedabad]]\n|Ahmedabad\n|-\n| [[Godrej Infotech]] \n|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n| [[Harbinger Systems]] \n|[[Pune]]\n|| Pune\n|-\n| [[Honeywell]] \n| [[Morris Plains, New Jersey]]\n|| Madurai\n|-\n| [[HSBC Bank India|HSBC GLT India]] \n|[[Pune]]\n|| Pune\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\"|[[IGATE]]\n| rowspan=\"8\"|[[Bridgewater Township, New Jersey]]\n|| Bangalore\n|-\n| Chennai\n|-\n| Gandhinagar\n|-\n| Hyderabad\n|-\n| Indore\n|-\n| Mumbai\n|-\n| Noida\n|-\n| Pune\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | [[KPIT Technologies]] \n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[Pune]]\n|| Pune\n|-\n|Noida\n|-\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|Chennai\n|-\n|Bengaluru\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Mastek]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n| Pune\n|-\n| [[Melstar Information Technologies]] \n|[[Mumbai]]\n|| Mumbai\n|-\n| [[Microland]] \n|[[Bangalore]]\n|| Bangalore\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\" | [[Microsoft India|Microsoft]] \n| rowspan=\"10\" |[[Hyderabad]]\n|-\n|Ahmedabad\n|-\n|Bangalore\n|-\n|Chennai\n|-\n|Gurgaon\n|-\n|Hyderabad\n|-\n|Kochi\n|-\n|Kolkata\n|-\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|New Delhi\n|-\n| [[Mistral Solutions]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Indian start-up Mistral Solutions finds business in developing technology for US defence and homeland security|url=http://e