\n| ''[[The Rothschilds (musical)|The Rothschilds]]''\n| Jacob Rothschilds\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Broadway\n|-\n| 1971\n| ''[[Two Gentlemen of Verona]]''\n| Proteus\n|-\n| 1977\n| ''[[Marco Polo Sings a Solo]]''\n| Tom Wintermouth\n| Off-Broadway\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Broadway]]{{dn|date=April 2020}}''\n| Performer\n| Broadway\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Woods (play)|The Woods]]''\n| Nick\n| Off-Broadway\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Censored Scenes From King Kong]]''\n| Benchgelter\n| Broadway\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[The Voice of the Turtle (play)|The Voice of the Turtle]]''\n| Bill Page\n| Off-Broadway\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Nick & Norma]]''\n| Performer\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Broadway\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[The Light in the Piazza (musical)|The Light in the Piazza]]''\n| Signor Naccarelli\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Cyrano de Bergerac]]''\n| Comte de Guiche\n| Broadway Revival\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Through a Glass Darkly]]{{dn|date=April 2020}}''\n| Performer\n| Off-Broadway\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[The Exonerated]]''\n| Karry Max Cook\n| Broadway\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Preludes]]{{dn|date=April 2020}}''\n| Chekhov, Tchaikovsky, Tolstoy, Glazunov, Tsar Nicholas II, The Master\n| Off-Broadway\n|}\n\n=== Music Videos ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Song\n!Artist\n!Role\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2002\n|[[Hands Clean]]\n|[[Alanis Morissette]]\n|Man At Bar\n|\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+Awards and nominations\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Title\n! Result\n|-\n| 1975\n| [[NYFCC Award]]\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 1976\n| [[Golden Globe]]\n| Best Acting Debut in a Motion Picture - Male\n| ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 1976\n| [[Oscar Award]]\n| Best Actor in a Supporting Role\n| ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 1986\n| [[Saturn Award]]\n| Best Actor\n| ''[[Fright Night]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 1992\n| Chainsaw Award\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| ''[[The Resurrected]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==